re":1,"quote":{"pid":"d58c349fe25602ffee325c6d3a7b5a66d829c528","tid":990412,"uid":39470,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"614ff26d930cf3bb2d8cb056817c24dbc7826b4c","tid":990412,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"但選韓國瑜係乜玩法?<br />\n<br />\n台豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"本來啲人都用選票倒向大陸<br />\n點知阿雜唔知做乜鳩走去提告台灣同胞書<br />\n捉到鹿都唔識脫角<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"阿雜直線思維。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d5cf0e0aa2993f16490c307698e582bc36bb02","tid":990412,"uid":34410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"問題係台灣d覺青有冇決心加入為獨立流血甚至付出生命先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你估支共真係俾你台灣up完獨立唔打你?"},{"pid":"37d995f40e6d76303f2053a01c980e783df3da4b","tid":990412,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"台狗選舉輸左又可以打飛機<br />\n下次選舉又收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57e9b6cc39c3f99fcc7f73b3752278b20abeb62","tid":990412,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03e0d5c337168c0e2f1080ad2f60bb76dd5d3dc8","tid":990412,"uid":52621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"614ff26d930cf3bb2d8cb056817c24dbc7826b4c","tid":990412,"uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:30:43.000Z","msg":"但選韓國瑜係乜玩法?<br />\n<br />\n台豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:38:42.000Z","msg":"又食又拎 兩家茶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:24:24.000Z","msg":"KMT係暗獨"},{"pid":"9813fe39c2362416a5c519d4c125aba74e9908f2","tid":990412,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"九合一國民黨大勝　中國網友驚呼：又要來騙錢騙物<br />\n<br />\n建立時間：2018/11/27 <br />\n<br />\n兩岸矚目的台灣「九合一」大選，在的國民黨大勝的情況下，周日（25日）凌晨「暫時落幕」。沒想到，這樣的選舉結果，反而讓許多中國網友不滿，擔心<span style=\"color: red;\">這些新當選的國民黨縣市長，又會靠著高喊「九二共識」，跑到中國「騙錢騙物」</span>。有人更感嘆，都快被川普搞到沒有餘糧了，還得被迫惠台。<br />\n<br />\n有長期觀察台灣政治的中國網友警告，很多台灣的縣市首長被國民黨奪下，其實是大大的不妙。未來可以預見，肯定又有一批國民黨的縣市首長，跑來大喊「九二共識」、「大家都是中國人」」「兩岸一家親」這樣的鬼話。然後靠這些話來騙錢騙物、騙吃騙喝，而「跪台辦」<span style=\"color: red;\">（國台辦）那幫廢物，一看到親中國的國民黨上門，鐵定不好意思拒絕，又會「高價」收購台灣的水果。也有網友提醒，國民黨本土派的本質，與民進黨沒什太大的區別，一個是暗獨，一個是明獨</span>。唯有全面封鎖台灣的「窮台政策」才有利於統一，而國民黨執政，反而難以執行「窮台政策」。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181127/1474033/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181127%2F1474033%2F&d=rYg5mx6yknX5c4F1CB4In%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=75fb7db1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181127%2F1474033%2F&h=27e3e046\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181127/1474033/</a>"},{"pid":"90110f7b50cc338631c6b2392b3cb4ed7ce35d3a","tid":990412,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cecdf4bcc5f476b719314fdc45f5907d11940287","tid":990412,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"一早話咗係繁體支那嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"姐係你認同台灣係支那一部份？<br />\n將台灣睇成支那一部份或直接當台灣係支那<br />\n思想上根本就同支那狗無大分別<br />\n吔屎啦機界賤種"},{"pid":"88890e7830d5f4eec8887ebfc9903dac0654ee18","tid":990412,"uid":2290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T19:26:48.000Z","msg":"上次公投台灣正名得45%贊成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf875292cfb242077194537e56221352fff